data.description: Charming Three Bedroom, Two Bath Home in Prime LocationWelcome to your new haven, nestled conveniently close to town! This delightful three-bedroom, two-bathroom residence offers a spacious great room with stunning vaulted ceilings, perfect for gatherings or serene relaxation.The kitchen boasts upgraded stainless steel appliances, ready to inspire your culinary adventures. Each bedroom comes with its own walk-in closet, providing ample storage space for all your needs.The master bath features a generously sized walk-in shower.Step outside to discover the inviting covered front porch, ideal for morning coffees and sunrise views. The open rear deck offers a wonderful space for outdoor entertaining and relaxation.As a bonus, the property includes an asphalt driveway and a convenient double carport, ensuring ease of access and parking.Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!** Buyer to verify all information & measurements before making an informed offer **
